text: Suzanne Raeth (26 March 1905 - 26 March 2001) was a French diver. She competed in the women's 3 metre springboard event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1905 births Category:2001 deaths Category:French female divers Category:Olympic divers of France Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Colmar
